                     <interp inst="t17450911-30-verdict157" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17450911-30-verdict157" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder40s"></interp>
               guilty of the felony, each 39 s
            </rs>.</p>
